<h1 id="privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</h1>

<h2 id="about">About</h2>

<p>Exile Companion (PoE) is an helper app providing information about the game content (players / items / ladder).</p>

<h2 id="disclaimer">Disclaimer</h2>
<p>This app is not the official Path of Exile application and is not related to Grinding Gear Games. It uses public and free APIs from different sources.</p>

<p>This app is not a game, just a tool.</p>

<h2 id="api-sources">API Sources</h2>
<p>Ladder &amp; Character API from the official Path of Exile website: https://www.pathofexile.com/developer/docs/api-resources</p>

<h2 id="resources">Resources</h2>
<p>Game Icons from the officiel @PathOfExile website. App icons by @FlatIcons &amp; @Freepik.</p>
